y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e9cf11865cb6b3320d702e710b37e0268f1547","tid":320400,"uid":4686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:57:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 完全一樣<br />\n<br />\n近排先大病完<br />\n因為連續2日食左M記 跟住喉嚨痛就開始仆街<br />\n依家病好 不過喉嚨都仲痛緊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且我唱完K 喉嚨都會好唔舒服 處理唔好又係會病<br />\n簡直係弱點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唱k 係玩命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a876e45cfa8c443f1c1ae3ebbcb31725096092","tid":320400,"uid":78060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:02:36.000Z","msg":"細個係咁,<br />\n大個可以食少少,<br />\n有冇人知點解一食熱氣野就會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73da44fca7760072f6cf62ce07dc6b20c606be9f","tid":320400,"uid":57643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:17:16.000Z","msg":"我都係一食就有暗瘡喉嚨痛飛滋，成身都覺得好乾好熱"},{"pid":"3f17d2ae4917725945717c80d81e340135a56774","tid":320400,"uid":4686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:30:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個係咁,<br />\n大個可以食少少,<br />\n有冇人知點解一食熱氣野就會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係外國會好d 唔知係咪d油同水既問題"},{"pid":"afb1e952d6e1d9640e4fbebf3f3759308dea7ad2","tid":320400,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:33:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係一食就有暗瘡喉嚨痛飛滋，成身都覺得好乾好熱</blockquote><br />\n食一包著片塊面就開始發熱<br />\n然後第二朝又多以粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲人係撚咁食都冇事<br />\n<br />\n公平咩？<span style=\"color: red;\"><span s